ZH: 1. 我不喜欢绕圈圈。
EN: I don't like to go in circles.
ZH: 2. 这条河绕过村庄流淌。
EN: The river winds around the village.
ZH: 3. 别绕远路，走捷径会更快。
EN: Don't take the long way around, taking a shortcut will be faster.
ZH: 4. 玛丽绕着玩具兔子转圈。
EN: Mary twirled around with her toy rabbit.
ZH: 5. 这条山路绕过了悬崖峭壁。
EN: This mountain road skirts around the cliffs.
ZH: 6. 他巧妙地绕过了对手的防守。
EN: He cleverly evaded the opponent's defense.
ZH: 7. 那个拳击手绕着拳台跑了几圈。
EN: The boxer ran a few laps around the ring.
ZH: 8. 我们不停地绕圈圈找到了出口。
EN: We kept circling until we found the exit.
ZH: 9. 孩子们绕着树玩耍。
EN: The children playfully run around the tree.
ZH: 10. 绕过那个大楼后面就是海滩。
EN: The beach is just around the corner of that building.
ZH: 11. 请绕过那片草地，那里有许多蚂蚁。
EN: Please avoid that patch of grass, it's full of ants.
ZH: 12. 小猫追逐着自己的尾巴绕圈圈。
EN: The kitten chases its own tail in circles.
ZH: 13. 这个地区的公共汽车路线绕过了市中心。
EN: The bus routes in this area bypass the city center.
ZH: 14. 他喜欢沿着海边散步，绕过了一座古老的灯塔。
EN: He enjoys walking along the coast, bypassing an old lighthouse.
ZH: 15. 这段道路绕过了山脚下的村庄。
EN: This road goes around the village at the foot of the mountain.
ZH: 16. 别绕来绕去，直接告诉我你的想法。
EN: Don't beat around the bush, tell me your thoughts directly.
ZH: 17. 这个公园有许多小径，供人们散步绕行。
EN: This park has many paths for people to walk and stroll around.
ZH: 18. 为了省时间，她决定绕过拥堵的交通路线。
EN: To save time, she decided to detour around the congested traffic route.
ZH: 19. 他选择绕了一个弯来避免冲突。
EN: He chose to take a detour to avoid conflict.
ZH: 20. 这段河流绕过了森林，形成了一个优美的弯曲。
EN: The river winds around the forest, forming a beautiful curve.
